snippet.title: Warzone 2100 - Video Game Trailer - PC Windows (1999)
snippet.description:
Warzone 2100 : official video game trailer. 
Developed by Pumpkin Studios
Published by Eidos Interactive in 1999 for PC Windows and Playstation.
 
Year :  1999 
System : PC (Windows), Playstation.

Video found on the coverdisk from the French magazine Generation 4 (issue #117, December 1998)
